  "description_snippet": "**VULNERABILITY DETAILS**   \nusrsctp_close and sctp_timeout_handler functions may run concurrently on separate threads(network[N] & usrsctplib timer[T] thread accordingly)  \nConsider the following scenario:  \n  so->so_count == 1  \n[N] user_socket.c:2018 executes the following: ACCEPT_LOCK(); SOCK_LO"
